{companyStockImages.map((image, index) => ( ))}
); } ShowCompany.propTypes = { companyLogo: PropTypes.string, companyName: PropTypes.string, companyAddress: PropTypes.string, companyContacts: PropTypes.string, companyEmail: PropTypes.string, companyWebsite: PropTypes.string, companyFax: PropTypes.string, companyDescription: PropTypes.string, companyCategory: PropTypes.string, companyStockImages: PropTypes.arrayOf(PropTypes.string), openingTime: PropTypes.string, closingTime: PropTypes.string, }; export default ShowCompany;
